				Chapter 2 - Drawing Down the Moon: Paragraph 1
			-
				-
					High Priestess stands in front of Altar, assumes Goddess position (arms
					crossed). Magus, kneeling in front of her, draws pentacle on her body with
					Phallus-headed Wand, invokes, "I Invoke and beseech Thee, O mighty Mother of
					all life and fertility. By seed and root, by stem and bud, by leaf and flower
					and fruit, by Life and Love, do I invoke Thee to descend into the body of thy
					servant and High Priestess [name]." The Moon having been drawn down, i.e., link
					established, Magus and other men give Fivefold Kiss:
